title: High Times Potluck
description:
High Times\&#039; Potluck (2002)

All bets are off when a high-profile artist is murdered over a mysterious suitcase and it\&#039;s prized contents in this outrageous comedy set amidst the dark, underground scene of Manhattan. As the coveted suitcase is sold, stolen, re-stolen and sold again, a bizarre assortment of characters including mobsters, punk rockers, artists, hippies and drag queens create hilarious havoc as their wacky lives intersect.
